description:
The simplest, quickest way to cook Adobo. Ready in 5 minutes! Plus a special guest to taste the dishes.

INGREDIENTS LIST:
3 tbsp coconut oil
4 cloves of garlic, crushed and minced
5-6 bunches of oyster mushrooms
pinch of sea salt



Fore more recipes and tips, visit http://astigvegan.com
